INTRODUCTION:

This program is a "proof of concept" presenting potential of using Monitis monitoring to XenServer or XCP hypervisors (with VMs).

For more information please visit Monitis blog: http://blog.monitis.com



LICENSE:

Please check the header of each file for details.


